# Rosemary's Birthday Celebration Website 🎉

A responsive, interactive birthday website with animations, countdown timer, and festive elements.

![Website Preview](screenshot.jpg) <!-- Add your screenshot here -->

## Features ✨

- **Dynamic Countdown Timer**
  - Automatically adjusts to next year if birthday has passed
  - Shows days, hours, minutes, seconds, and milliseconds
  - Displays target date with year

- **Festive Animations**
  - Floating flowers 🌸
  - Fireworks explosion effects 🎆
  - Flickering candle flames 🕯️
  - Typing animation on title
  - Background color transitions

- **Media Integration**
  - Embedded YouTube video (auto-plays on birthday)
  - Music widget integration
  - Responsive video container

- **Interactive Elements**
  - Pull-to-refresh functionality (mobile)
  - Auto-refresh every 5 minutes
  - Scrollable content
  - Mobile-responsive design

- **Visual Effects**
  - Glowing text effects
  - Bouncing animations
  - Confetti-like elements
  - Gradient backgrounds

## Technologies Used 💻

- **Frontend**
  - HTML5
  - CSS3 (Animations, Flexbox, Grid)
  - JavaScript (ES6)

- **Third-Party Integrations**
  - YouTube Embedded Player
  - Mdundo Music Widget
  - Google Fonts (Lobster, Party MT)

